---
title: Green Goddess Noodles with Fresh Peas, Broccoli and Toasted Cashews
description: Summer is in full swing, and we've got the perfect Green Goddess Noodles for a patio dinner. Tender crips peas, bright broccoli and soba noodles all get tossed in our zippy herb dressing!
